						<summary>

						<p>On a pillar planted in front of the Veṅkaṭēśvarasvāmi temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1187, Makarasaṅkrānti.</p>						

						<p>Records the gift of 50 cows for burning a perpetual lamp in the temple of Mūlasthāna-Mallēśvara at Telkicheṟla by Yaṟapōtapeddi. The gift was entrusted to Nārebōya for supply of ghee to the temple.</p>						

						</summary>
